    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n    <strong>School</strong>&nbsp;transmutation&nbsp;(polymorph);\n    <strong>Level</strong>&nbsp;alchemist 4, bard 4, magus 4, medium 4, psychic 4, shaman 4, sorcerer/wizard 4, summoner 4, unchained Summoner 4, witch 4;\n    \n    \n    \n    \n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Casting Time</strong>&nbsp;1 standard action<br>\n    <strong>Components</strong>&nbsp;V, S, M (a small piece of doppelganger flesh)<br>\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Range</strong>&nbsp;personal<br>\n    \n    <strong>Targets</strong>&nbsp;you<br>\n    \n    <strong>Duration</strong>&nbsp;1 minute/level (D)<br>\n    \n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  <p>This spell functions as <i><i>alter</i> self</i>, except you can as a swift action <i>alter</i> the disguise (within the limitations of <i><i>alter</i> self</i>).</p><p>For example, you could transform yourself into a halfling, then a lizardfolk, then an elf, and so on. You can change your form a number of times equal to your caster level.</p>\n</div>\n",
